<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light dark">
    <title>Confirmación de Orden</title>
    <style>
        :root { color-scheme: light dark; }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

        .header {
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            padding: 24px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header img { height: 44px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto; }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 12px 0 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .content {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 24px;
            border: 1px solid #cccccc;
        }

        .content > p { color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 16px; }

        .order-info {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .order-info h3 {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .order-info p { margin: 6px 0; color: #333333; }

        .order-items { margin: 16px 0; }
        .order-items h3 { font-size: 15px; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 8px; }

        .item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .item-name { font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
        .item-qty { font-size: 13px; color: #555555; }

        .item-price {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .totals { margin: 8px 0 0; text-align: right; }
        .totals p { margin: 4px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; }

        .totals .total-final {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 2px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .phone-highlight {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 6px 0;
        }

        .hours { font-size: 13px; color: #555555; margin: 6px 0; }

        .map-link { color: #2563eb; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }

        .button-wrap { text-align: center; margin: 16px 0 4px; }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 13px 32px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #777777;
            font-size: 12px;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
        }

        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            body { background-color: #121212 !important; color: #e8e8e8 !important; }
            .wrapper { background-color: #121212; }
            .header { background-color: #1e3a8a !important; }
            .content { background-color: #1e1e1e !important; border-color: #333333 !important; }
            .content > p { color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
            .order-info { background-color: #2a2a2a !important; border-color: #3a3a3a !important; }
            .order-info h3 { color: #93c5fd !important; border-color: #3a3a3a !important; }
            .order-info p { color: #cccccc !important; }
            .order-items h3 { color: #f0f0f0 !important; }
            .item { border-color: #3a3a3a !important; color: #cccccc !important; }
            .item-name { color: #f0f0f0 !important; }
            .item-qty { color: #aaaaaa !important; }
            .item-price { color: #f0f0f0 !important; }
            .totals p { color: #cccccc !important; }
            .totals .total-final { color: #93c5fd !important; border-color: #93c5fd !important; }
            .phone-highlight { color: #f0f0f0 !important; background-color: #333333 !important; }
            .hours { color: #aaaaaa !important; }
            .map-link { color: #93c5fd !important; }
            .footer { background-color: #121212 !important; color: #888888 !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Constru-ir" />
        <h1>¡Gracias por tu compra!</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>Hola <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>Hemos recibido tu orden y está siendo procesada.</p>

        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>Información de la Orden</h3>
            <p><strong>Número de Orden:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Fecha:</strong> {{orderDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Estado:</strong> {{orderStatus}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="order-items">
            <h3>Artículos de tu Orden</h3>
            {{#each items}}
            <div class="item">
                <div>
                    <div class="item-name">{{this.productName}}</div>
                    <div class="item-qty">Cantidad: {{this.quantity}} × ${{this.price}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="item-price">${{this.subtotal}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}

            <div class="totals">
                <p>Subtotal: ${{subtotal}}</p>
                {{#if tax}}<p>Impuestos: ${{tax}}</p>{{/if}}
                {{#if shipping}}<p>Envío: ${{shipping}}</p>{{/if}}
                <p class="total-final">Total: ${{total}}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        {{#if isPickup}}
        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>📍 Retiro en Tienda</h3>
            <p><strong>{{store.name}}</strong></p>
            <p>{{store.address}}<br>{{store.city}}</p>
            <p><span class="phone-highlight">📞 {{store.phone}}</span></p>
            <p class="hours">🕐 {{store.hours}}</p>
            {{#if store.mapUrl}}
            <p><a href="{{store.mapUrl}}" class="map-link">Ver en el mapa →</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        {{else}}
        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>📦 Dirección de Envío</h3>
            <p><strong>{{shippingAddress.firstName}} {{shippingAddress.lastName}}</strong><br>
            {{shippingAddress.address}}<br>
            {{shippingAddress.city}}, {{shippingAddress.state}} {{shippingAddress.zipCode}}<br>
            {{shippingAddress.country}}</p>
            <p><span class="phone-highlight">📞 {{shippingAddress.phone}}</span></p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>💳 Información de Pago</h3>
            <p><strong>Método:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
            <div class="button-wrap">
                <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" class="button">Ver mi Orden</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        {{#if notes}}
        <div class="order-info">
            <h3>📝 Notas</h3>
            <p>{{notes}}</p>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Este es un correo automático, por favor no respondas a este mensaje.</p>
        <p>Si tienes alguna pregunta, contáctanos.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
